    "For instance, they might start to explore what aspects of a sentence the attention heads in a transformer-based model are emphasizing by giving it higher scores.",
    "The autonomy of these language models also shows in the general scope of their applicability.",
    "Pre-trained transformer-based LLMs are general-purpose language models that can quickly and again autonomously adapt to new environments and challenges.",
    "Here, too, the models are not dependent on receiving instruction from outside, typically from humans.",
    "Rather, they autonomously, and very quickly, adapt to the new specific task at hand."
